{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Powerful Special Skills by Robot</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103700/extras/\u110f\u1169\u1103\u1173\u110b\u1175\u1100\u1173\u11af_\u1111\u1175\u11af\u1109\u1161\u11af\u1100\u1175_\u110f\u1173\u11af\u1105\u1175\u11b8.gif?t=1728955581\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Robots have unique special skills that excel in emergency situations and when facing large numbers of enemies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">These special skills can be charged through experience points, capsules, and merchants after clearing stages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Main Weapons for Each Robot</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103700/extras/1_\u1105\u1169\u1107\u1169\u11ba_\u1109\u1165\u11ab\u1110\u1162\u11a8_\u1106\u1175\u11be_\u110c\u116e\u1106\u116e\u1100\u1175_\u1107\u1167\u11ab\u1100\u1167\u11bc.gif?t=1728955581\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each robot can utilize three main weapons, with two skill trees available for each main weapon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use the formations of sub weapons to create your own unique weapon formation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>In the demo version, only one type of robot can be used.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Growth Through Leveling Up</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103700/extras/\u1109\u1173\u110f\u1175\u11af\u110f\u1161\u1103\u1173_\u110e\u1161\u11bc_\u110f\u1173\u11af\u1105\u1175\u11b8.gif?t=1728955581\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">By defeating enemies in stages, you gain experience points.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Reaching certain experience thresholds allows you to level up and choose skill cards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Various Bosses</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103700/extras/\u1107\u1169\u1109\u11738\u110c\u1169\u11bc_\u110f\u1173\u11af\u1105\u1175\u11b8.gif?t=1728955581\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Face off against unique bosses across a total of 10 stages, each with their own distinct characteristics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>In the demo version, you can progress up to stage 5.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Tense Boss Battles and Diverse Attack Patterns</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103700/extras/\u1107\u1162\u11ab\u1109\u1175_3\u110c\u1169\u11bc_\u1110\u1173\u11a8\u1109\u1165\u11bc_\u1100\u1169\u11bc\u1100\u1167\u11a8_\u110f\u1173\u11af\u1105\u1175\u11b8.gif?t=1728955581\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No two bosses are the same, and most will randomly use one of three special attack patterns, providing enjoyment even in repeated playthroughs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Growth Elements - Robots and Main Weapons</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103700/extras/2_\u1105\u1169\u1107\u1169\u11ba_\u110b\u1165\u11b8\u1100\u1173\u1105\u1166\u110b\u1175\u1103\u1173.gif?t=1728955581\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Upgrade your robot\u2019s stats and traits using in-game currency gained from gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can also unlock and enhance weapon skills to see changes in combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Growth Elements - Sub Weapons</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/ste